Class HistoryModel

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
count.gui.AnnotatedTableModel
count.gui.HistoryModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
class HistoryModel
extends AnnotatedTableModel
TableModel for ancestral reconstructions with one row for each family: lists-of-columns for lineage-specific statistics, and arithmetically defined columns.
Author:
csuros
